title: Molly Hatchet - Live In Hamburg 2004 - DVD - cOOt
description:
Filmed at the Hamburg Harley Days, July 24, 2004 before a more than enthusiastic crowd, Molly Hatchet perform a set featuring all of their classics, treating the audience to a dynamic and exhilarating show.
